playstore_details.description:
OCB iOTP, is Soft OTP Advanced application, was built by OCB for secure your online transactions based on Policy of The State Bank of Viet Nam.
 
For submit transaction on OCB Online/ OCB OMNI, Customer will use the OCB iOTP application to protect and authorize your online financial transaction by OTP (One Time Password) that be generated by encryption method as combination Transaction ID. Condition, customer need to install OCB iOTP app and activate your app with Activation Code that supplied by OCB when you register to use OCB service at OCB’s branches.
 
You must to register Soft OTP Advanced service with OCB’s bank and install app for using. Moreover, You can register service on OCB Online/OCB OMNI  (just applied for individual customer).
 
For further information, please feel free contact our Customer service via hotline 1800 6678 or access website www.ocb.com.vn
 
OCB iOTP – Security, Simplicity, Quickly
